  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\"><img alt=\"House Rogers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Rogers.svg/50px-House_Rogers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Rogers.svg/75px-House_Rogers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/House_Rogers.svg/100px-House_Rogers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Harrold Rogers</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\"><img alt=\"House Rogers.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Rogers.svg/50px-House_Rogers.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1b/House_Rogers.svg/75px-House_Rogers.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1b/House_Rogers.svg/100px-House_Rogers.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Title_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Title-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\">House Rogers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Branda_Stark\" title=\"Branda Stark\">Branda Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (appendix)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Harrold Rogers</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\">House Rogers</a> during the first half of the third century after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Title_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Title-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harrold_Rogers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Harrold married <a href=\"/index.php/Branda_Stark\" title=\"Branda Stark\">Branda Stark</a>, the first cousin of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edwyle_Stark\" title=\"Edwyle Stark\">Edwyle Stark</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_appendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_appendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Harrold_Rogers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Title-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Title_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Title_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">asoiaf.westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/152844-the-wiki-timeline-project-v2/&amp;page=5&amp;tab=comments#comment-8495418\">The Wiki-Timeline Project v2 &#8211; Comment by Ran (March 16, 2020)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_appendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_appendix:_stark_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Appendix: Stark Lineage.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403120956\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.077 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.277 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 443/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10448/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5326/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 456/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1271/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.35 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  268.338      1 -total\n 97.67%  262.080      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.89%  259.996      1 Template:Infobox\n 13.46%   36.121     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  6.07%   16.292      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.44%    3.860      1 Template:Ref\n  0.98%    2.637      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.70%    1.867      1 Template:Re